text: Zhang Liming (born 27 November 1957) is a Chinese rowing coxswain. She competed in the women's coxed four event at the 1984 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1957 births Category:Living people Category:Chinese female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of China Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Coxswains (rowing)
